knowledge_graph.title: Cedar River BBQ
knowledge_graph.merchant_description: "Cedar River BBQ has been a part of the Renton community since 2000, serving up some of the best barbecues in town. We are located in the heart of downtown Renton and pride ourselves on being a terrific lunch and dinner spot for individuals working there. Our menu offers traditional and non-traditional Texas Style Barbecue, using the best meats and ingredients to create a mouth-watering dining experience. Everything is slow-smoked to perfection, from brisket to ribs and pulled pork."
